{"tid":557501,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港快運批A320Neo可能被歐洲航空安全局要求停飛","createTime":"2018-02-11T12:02:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-11T15:46:05.000Z","uid":51271,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f0fc082362d5a0d118f741a01f17743b830ae3dc","tid":557501,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T12:02:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://avherald.com/h?article=4b4c4509&amp;opt=256\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Favherald.com%2Fh%3Farticle%3D4b4c4509%26opt%3D256&d=Vm%2BvChM2uigGI6EO2m2XkgRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=7be9ceaa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://avherald.com/h?article=4b4c4509&amp;opt=256</a><br />\n<br />\n事緣上星期美國有隻A320Neo with PW engine飛飛下狂震，而家發現好似係飛飛下fan blade打爛o野，而家歐洲航空安全局要求部份A320neo with PW engine，又有做左改裝o既飛機，若果兩隻engine都係有改就全面停飛，只有一隻engine改的話就暫時無ETOPS。<br />\n<br />\n有d航空新聞網站就話有大約43隻engine受到影響，但無講去左邊個客手上。<br />\n<br />\n香港快運而家有四隻A320neo，四隻都係PW engine，有一隻應該已經ground o左一段時間，真係唔知UO會唔會再中一球。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e63cf91a262babad72adf89a9b6cba80a3d18004","tid":557501,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T12:31:02.000Z","msg":"因航就叻叻 揀cfm"},{"pid":"68cfef1b255f50ffa7fb14ee374f70482f9ceb6b","tid":557501,"uid":57677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T12:37:12.000Z","msg":"hkexpress 有去歐洲？"},{"pid":"b18c75a42acadc952f514c3945f04926c8d69749","tid":557501,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"68cfef1b255f50ffa7fb14ee374f70482f9ceb6b","tid":557501,"uid":57677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T12:37:12.000Z","msg":"hkexpress 有去歐洲？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T13:30:16.000Z","msg":"A320N SoD (State of Design)係法國，即係由EASA規管，各國民航管理局都係睇FAA + EASA做人"},{"pid":"6a